Interface JavaStackFrame

All Known Implementing Classes:
DTFJJavaStackFrame, JavaStackFrame, JCJavaStackFrame, PHDCorruptJavaStackFrame, PHDJavaStackFrame
public interface JavaStackFrame
Represents a frame on a Java thread stack.
